<HEADLINE> 13 Killed in Traffic Accident in Turkey </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, December 24 (Xinhua) -- Thirteen people were killed and
at least 15 others injured Wednesday night when a passenger bus
collided with a oil tanker in northern Turkey, the Anatolia News
Agency reported Thursday morning.
</P>
<P>
