the Black Sea, setting the tanker aflame, the report said.
</P>
<P>
Fire-fighters rushed to the traffic scene and put out the
tanker fire, said the agency.
</P>
<P>
The injured were taken to nearby hospitals for treatment.
</P>
<P>
An investigation into the cause of the accident is underway.
