<HEADLINE> Chinese Farmers Doing Better after Moving from Dam Site (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The municipal government plans to spend 200 million yuan over 3
years building 1,700 km of roads for these migrant people, and has
paved 300 km of roads around which 2,000 of them live.
</P>
<P>
