Chittagong Urea Fertilizer Ltd. and the Kharnaphuli Fertilizer
Company.
</P>
<P>
The main objective of setting up the two DAP plants is to
maximize the use of DAP fertilizer in the country. On completion,
the two plants will produce 240,000 tons of DAP fertilizer
annually. 
