defense industries, which have been rationalizing their
activities in recent years in order to better confront their
competitors, especially in the United States.
</P>
<P>
Alenia Space Co. has 2,750 employees and in 1997 made 998
billion lire (624 million U.S. dollars). In 1998 that figure is
expected to rise to 1,065 billion lire (665 million U.S.
dollars). 
