China's mobile phone and base station system equipment market
since it first imported mobile-phone technology in 1990. It set up
a development center in California's Silicon Valley in the United
States last year.
</P>
<P>
Official forecasts expect 15 million more mobile-phone users in
China next year. Hangzhou Oriental has said it will strive to
develop more than 10 competitive models each year.  
