<HEADLINE> Indonesia to Reshuffle National Badminton Team </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JAKARTA, December 24 (Xinhua) -- The Badminton Association of
Indonesia (PBSI) plans to reshuffle its national players as it
prepares to win gold medals at the 2000 Olympics Games in Sydney,
PBSI secretary general Leo Chandra Wiranata said on Wednesday.
