expected to increase by three percent on the 1997 level.
</P>
<P>
"Xinhua Daily Telegraph"
</P>
<P>
--Chinese legislators drawing up the draft Contract Law have
decided against introducing elements which would have permitted
contractors to challenge details of the contract, and even have it
annulled.
</P>
