friendly match at home to Denmark in January, Colombia's first
game since the World Cup finals, their first under new coach
Javier Alvarez and their first since the international retirement
of Carlos Valderrama.
</P>
<P>
Parma's Asprilla was sent home after Colombia's first World
Cup match in France for publicly criticising coach Hernan Dario
Gomez, who resigned after the competition, and other members of
the squad. 
</P>
</TEXT>
