<TEXT>
<P>
KHARTOUM, December 23 (Xinhua) -- Hassan Abdulla al Turabi was
unanimously re-elected Speaker of the Sudanese National Assembly
(Parliament) at a parliamentary session Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
