not only executive bodies but also of the general public at
large.
</P>
<P>
Ethiopia's forest resource has depleted from 40 percent about
a century ago to only two percent now.
</P>
<P>
Some 100,000 to 150,000 hectares of land is deforested
annually in the country, said sources from the three-day meeting.
